435
00:22:41,871 --> 00:22:42,997
Đúng không, Timon?

436
00:22:43,072 --> 00:22:44,562
Đúng đấy, anh bạn.

437
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,505
<i>♪ Ingonyama ♪</i>

438
00:22:46,575 --> 00:22:49,806
